# Permutation of all forms of construction
# when fusing a box and a prism

box ba 3 3 0 5 7 4

# prism from right

vertex v1 4 2 0
vertex v2 4 3 0
vertex v3 4 3 1
vertex v4 4 2 1

edge ea v1 v2
edge eb v2 v3
edge ec v3 v4
edge ed v4 v1

wire w ea eb ec ed
mkplane f w

prism bb f -1 0 0


bfuse result ba bb

checkprops result -s 170
checkview -display result -2d -otherwise { ba bb } -s -path ${imagedir}/${test_image}.png